                <seg>
                    <tei:milestone xml:id="UT22084-091-074-45"/>“Monks, the Thus-Gone Aparimitāyus’ king of trees is the tree called Radiating Jeweled Lotus, and it is covered in flowers and fruit.</seg>
            </tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
            <prop type="folio">F.222.a</prop>
            <prop type="location-id">UT22084-091-074-45</prop>
