            </tuv>
	<tuv xml:lang="en">
                <seg>[“Monks, any monk, nun, male lay practitioner, or female lay practitioner who bears in mind the name of the Thus-Gone Aparimitāyus] will never have to face any [dangers from fire, dangers from water, dangers from poison,] dangers from weapons,</seg>
