            </tuv>
	<tuv xml:lang="en">
                <seg>[“Monks, any monk, nun, male lay practitioner, or female lay practitioner who bears in mind the name of the Thus-Gone Aparimitāyus] will never have to face any [dangers from fire, dangers from water, dangers from poison, dangers from weapons, dangers from yakṣas, and] dangers from rākṣasas,</seg>
            </tuv>
</tu>
<tu>
            <prop type="folio">F.222.a</prop>
            <prop type="location-id">UT22084-091-074-46</prop>
	<tuv xml:lang="bo">
                <seg>སྔོན་གྱི་ལས་ཀྱི་རྣམ་པར་སྨིན་པ་ནི་གང་ལ་ཡང་མ་གཏོགས་སོ། །</seg>
            </tuv>
